<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢١٣]</span> أَبُو حاضِرٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سمِعَ ابنَ عَبّاسٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رَوى عنْه أَبُو السَّوّارِ السُّلميُّ وعَمرُو بنُ مَيمونٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سمِعَ ابنَ عَبّاسٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
